e CREAM measurements turn out to be\nsmall, unless somewhat unrealistic propagation parameters are assumed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Nov 2016 16:55:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-05"}
