mB = 12\n+/- 16 MJup. L2 Pup B is most likely a planet or low mass brown dwarf with an\norbital period around 5 years. Its continuum brightness and molecular emission\nsuggest that it may be surrounded by an extended molecular atmosphere or an\naccretion disk. L2 Pup therefore emerges as a promising vantage point on the\ndistant future of our Solar System.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Nov 2016 21:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-22"}
