ation induced\nin the considered experiments is relatively modest, with effects that depend on\ntype of transfer function of the original devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 19 Nov 2016 12:35:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-22"}
